Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 不去学校吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家很担心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能说句话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说话也找不到解决的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就差不多这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是因为身体不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.30,0:03:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 老师明天还会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了很好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图象上传到留言版上了 请看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.70,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没去学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也没能体会到我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如何也没法喜欢上老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他为什么要对我那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银莲花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}银莲花花语是凄凉与寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是见个面可以么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师他也有自己的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我放学回家经常路过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情也会平静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实生活中 这些事情我没告诉过任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和银莲花之间的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 让我听听你的声音也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.00,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的地方竟然可以让心情平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 家里似乎也没有容身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.30,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 正在那个废墟的庭院中给你发邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校里遇到不顺心的事 感到很沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天也不会去学校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.00,0:05:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把怨恨的对象的名字写上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女就会为你消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜我终于找到了网站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犹豫要不要写上老师的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写上去也没什么不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你同情老师吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.20,0:06:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说不定也希望这样的事发生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 像我这种人不知道能不能帮上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木老师说你是个很热心的老师呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热心不代表有能力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为并非如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家 安静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是记者柴田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.60,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为了采访一些教育问题将旁听我们的课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并问一些问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好配合柴田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我是柴田一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我不会打扰大家上课 请多关…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 安静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很老实呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真得觉得大家和普通学生没什么两样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上明明话那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是交际吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交际
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.30,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.50,0:08:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是朋友来搭话的时候就回几句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那时候老师正在说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老师是大人了 所以我们认为没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.60,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是乖乖地听老师的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后不知道要被别人说什么闲话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.70,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦 最近的孩子都是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.80,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们有听说过地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是传言吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索了也没找到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.80,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说过有人登录上吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家压力都很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁都想诅咒那么一两个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那种传言才会流传开来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上他们都是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别说大话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也知道地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个虽然听到过一两句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有去登录过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.20,0:10:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想老师可能也有想要诅咒的一两个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田先生 真正的取材目的不会是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要诅咒的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那情况或许正相反吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 那么我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深泽老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 听说你班上的泽井还没有来上学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好办啊 如果不好好教导的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是去保健室躺着也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也算是来上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来可是很麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系到学校的信誉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆让她退学算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没成果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.50,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁 都生活在事与愿违的人生中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而像你这个年龄更是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个你也明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到学校来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的话会轻松一点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我也一直在考虑你烦恼些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实上 一开始你不是也过得很开心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说点什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说我就什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说了 你也不会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.20,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像老师这样没有任何疑问 认真工作的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着普通人的生活的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情你也不会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室中的人际关系很复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道是我不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道那么做不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必须迎合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样反复着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没想到过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为大家只是喜欢这样才这样做的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去开心也是表面现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说老师不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再管我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把我的事放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 如果我不去学校你会很为难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上有不去上学的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的处境就很为难 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为自己很了解吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为自己是特殊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有考虑到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只考虑自己的处境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我来这里也是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任催着我解决你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子啊 全是面子问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那样说话 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能让妈妈太担心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.40,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该如何是好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.30,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自己不好 还是周围的人不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在想着同样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该怎么办好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索性真的就不再去学校了呢 还是去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你来学校那么多次的明明是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你来了却反而变得有些不安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.10,0:15:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 老师坦白了自己的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深泽老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜我现在在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都无法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家以后再发邮件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.70,0:16:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我是银莲花才跟我发邮件的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.80,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一惊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银莲花竟然就是泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想要欺骗你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有其他发泄的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果什么都不做早就承受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学生时期不明白不上学的人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当上教师后开始理解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和老师交流才让我解脱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.90,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.70,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我在地狱通信上写了老师的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了吗 地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得是个非常寂寞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见见她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把我送进地狱去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疲惫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想轻松一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经厌倦了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深泽好像有些不正常呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.80,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为想装聪明而导致有点失常吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想见到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要怎么说才明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是帮助学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.20,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是提高不了升学率又有什么前途可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是跟差生来往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全班成绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.70,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能去地狱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.60,0:20:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 可知道自己的所做意味着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我缔结了契约的人无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.20,0:20:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后 其灵魂将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你自作聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去地狱游山玩水吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我之后也会去那的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.10,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等着我 在地狱的深渊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.00,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.10,0:21:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪了 深泽老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是个热心的老师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是认真过头了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他别一时冲动做了什么错事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.80,0:21:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类还是难以理解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.70,0:21:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个热血老师失踪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.10,0:22:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.00,0:22:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然现在的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.70,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.40,0:22:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地狱当作极乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了啊 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.70,0:22:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人说好那就可以了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.50,0:22:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后事你不必去考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.10,0:22:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.30,0:22:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的地方竟然可以让心情平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.00,0:22:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和银莲花之间的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.20,0:22:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的
